          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Before your implementation of "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/urlsessiontaskdelegate/1411595-urlsession"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " uses this initializer to create a server trust credential, you are responsible for evaluating the received "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/sectrust"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " instance. You get this "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/urlprotectionspace/1409926-servertrust"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " from the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/urlauthenticationchallenge/1410012-protectionspace"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " of the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/urlauthenticationchallenge"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " parameter that is passed to your delegate method. Pass the trust instance to "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/1394363-sectrustevaluate"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " to evaluate it. If this call indicates the trust is invalid, you should cancel the challenge by passing the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/urlsession/authchallengedisposition/cancelauthenticationchallenge"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " disposition to the completion handler."
            }
          ]
        }
